Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.82,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(359,363)}Silence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corner of a page in this murderer's notebook appears to have been torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would a person still die if their name was written on the torn-off part?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? {\alpha&HFF&}I've never used it that way, so I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? I've never used it that way, so I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is it true that Shinigami only eat apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a Shinigami's internal organs are retrogressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, in fact, they've evolved such that we no longer need to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally been freed, and yet you never leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when Misa-san comes to see you, you only chat for a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said that you're free to take your romance outside now, I meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira case is far from over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm hardly in the mood for romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you saying that you've got a problem with me always being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm not in a position where I can judge criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}I want you to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, I want you to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}let's build a new world, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... let's build a new world, together.
