Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:55.87,INSERT-english,,0000,0000,0000,,please hold his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:04:00.09,INSERT-english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm on my own far away,
