Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more criminals being killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday alone, there was 16...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them were broadcast as criminals after Higuchi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one after the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that Higuchi wasn't Kira after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We know for a fact that until Higuchi was captured, he was the one judging criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that yet another Kira has made an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is the only possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This began the instant Amane was freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, I can't believe you're still saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're talking about "the instant" this started, that was when Higuchi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case, if there is someone out there using a second notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely catch that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami said she didn't know, {\alpha&HFF&}but if it's possible to kill someone using paper torn out from the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami said she didn't know, but if it's possible to kill someone using paper torn out from the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once someone writes a name in this notebook, they need to write another name within 13 days or they'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light and Amane Misa are still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13 days... {\alpha&HFF&}this is the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13 days... this is the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ryuuzaki, even if we manage to catch the person who's writing names in the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you actually be able to charge them of mass murder and get a conviction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! They wrote a lot of people's names in the notebook knowing that those people would die as a result!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't make the notebook public knowledge like that, we should obliterate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obliteration isn't the calmest solution to the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the higher-ups will opt for a solution similar to that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can prove the murders resulted from the notebook, it'll be the death penalty, or at the very least, life imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more or less how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Yagami Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa gets caught, then you'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's it! {\alpha&HFF&}This guy is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's it! This guy is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light is certain that I'll save Misa's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, the only way to save Misa {\alpha&HFF&}is to write Ryuuzaki's real name in my own notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, the only way to save Misa is to write Ryuuzaki's real name in my own notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I kill Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll undeniably have interfered with Misa's lifespan, {\alpha&HFF&}and will also die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll undeniably have interfered with Misa's lifespan, and will also die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all set up for the benefit of Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that you're a Shinigami, I know you're into Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'll stand by and let Misa die after her lifespan has just been halved again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of Misa's happiness.
Comment: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's nothing worth mentioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of bells...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the bells sound incredibly noisy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been ringing incessantly today; {\alpha&HFF&}I can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been ringing incessantly today; I can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's a wedding at a church, or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense. Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. {\alpha&HFF&}Everything I say is made up on the spot, so please don't believe a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Everything I say is made up on the spot, {\alpha&HFF&}so please don't believe a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Everything I say is made up on the spot, so please don't believe a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}The majority of what you say isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Ryuuzaki. The majority of what you say isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I took it all seriously, there'd be no end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}the same applies to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... the same applies to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever uttered a single completely true thing since you were born?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly I lie every now and then, {\alpha&HFF&}but surely no one can be truthful throughout their entire life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly I lie every now and then, but surely no one can be truthful throughout their entire life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People aren't that perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, {\alpha&HFF&}I've made a point of not telling lies that will hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I've made a point of not telling lies that will hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back inside. {\alpha&HFF&}We're both soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back inside. We're both soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. That was quite an ordeal, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault for being out in that downpour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd help. You seem to be drying yourself with quite some fervor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You don't have to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw in a massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least allow me to atone for this. I'm not at all bad at it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get used to it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nearly time to say farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll be there straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, I'll be there straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go then, Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like things have gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, what's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got permission from a ruined country to use the notebook in an execution?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please begin the arrangements to transport the notebook at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to test the notebook for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is absurd! There's no need to do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know that the power of the notebook is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, who is going to write the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you do, you have to write in it every 13 days for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who will write the name in the notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}will be someone who's already been sentenced to die within 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who will write the name in the notebook... will be someone who's already been sentenced to die within 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do a probationary deal, saying that if they're alive after 13 days, they'll be removed from death row.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... people's lives--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we manage to clarify this, it'll take us straight to the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! {\alpha&HFF&}W-What's happening?! A power cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-{\alpha&HFF&}What's happening?! A power cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-What's happening?! {\alpha&HFF&}A power cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-What's happening?! A power cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deletion of data? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I instructed Watari to delete all the data if something were to happen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If something were to happen to him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it... I can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the Shiniga--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki!! {\alpha&HFF&}What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki!! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki? What's the matter? Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Ryuuzaki? {\alpha&HFF&}What's the matter? Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Ryuuzaki? What's the matter? {\alpha&HFF&}Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Ryuuzaki? What's the matter? Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki... and now us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}and now us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, Ryuuzaki... and now us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck! {\alpha&HFF&}Where's that Shinigami?! Show yourself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck! Where's that Shinigami?! {\alpha&HFF&}Show yourself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck! Where's that Shinigami?! Show yourself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-{\alpha&HFF&}Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know something about this! {\alpha&HFF&}Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know something about this! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should look as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi, we'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, {\alpha&HFF&}whatever's going on here... I will avenge Ryuuzaki's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, whatever's going on here... {\alpha&HFF&}I will avenge Ryuuzaki's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, whatever's going on here... I will avenge Ryuuzaki's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solving this case is the only way to bid him farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Watari, and the other victims too... {\alpha&HFF&}for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Watari, and the other victims too... for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we'll be killed! {\alpha&HFF&}Isn't that what this has been about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we'll be killed! Isn't that what this has been about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san, {\alpha&HFF&}if you're scared of being killed, then I suggest you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san, if you're scared of being killed, then I suggest you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This team is composed of men willing to give their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, well, I guess you're right... {\alpha&HFF&}but don't say it how Ryuuzaki would, Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, well, I guess you're right... but don't say it how Ryuuzaki would, Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my obstacles have been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\alpha&HFF&}am the god of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the god of a new world.
